history.content:
We are still working on finding a room and time for this class to be offered. Instead of posting incorrect information in the schedule, we have taken the class off the schedule until we have accurate information.

THIS CLASS WILL BE OFFERED IN F19! Once we have finalized the meeting day/time and room, we will re-post it on classes.berkeley.edu.

Yes, we know that phase 1 begins on 4/15 and we are doing our best to resolve the situation as quickly as we can so you can plan your schedule for Fall.
history.subject: F19: CS 189/289A - class WILL be offered but is not listed in schedule yet
